| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3128 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 35911884-ba8d-5a4a-9012-cf2fe4350d41"
